@runId = YOUR_RUN_ID

### Start the ExpenseReimbursement workflow
POST http://localhost:7071/api/workflows/ExpenseReimbursement/run
Content-Type: text/plain

EXP-2025-042

### Check workflow status and pending approvals
GET http://localhost:7071/api/workflows/ExpenseReimbursement/status/{{runId}}

### Submit manager approval
POST http://localhost:7071/api/workflows/ExpenseReimbursement/respond/{{runId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"eventName": "ManagerApproval", "response": {"approved": true, "comments": "Looks good"}}

### Submit budget approval
POST http://localhost:7071/api/workflows/ExpenseReimbursement/respond/{{runId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"eventName": "BudgetApproval", "response": {"approved": true, "comments": "Within budget"}}

### Submit compliance approval
POST http://localhost:7071/api/workflows/ExpenseReimbursement/respond/{{runId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"eventName": "ComplianceApproval", "response": {"approved": true, "comments": "Compliant"}}
